    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.poster.avif?t=1734953793\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.webm?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278230/extras/be1591ef0a7c6a914dda1d0edd19acad.mp4?t=1734953793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity Block 2 是一款简约的益智游戏，玩家必须控制环境才能让方块到达终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用物理优势，控制 街区 周围的环境。适时转弯，否则你将后悔莫及！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 个手工制作的关卡。从最简单的关卡到让你泪流满面的关卡！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松的音乐（这样你就不会因为更难的关卡而更加烦躁）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam 成就</p></li></ul>",
